11, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC 5 free wherever you are The lawyer, Audrey Msellati, said in a letter posted to theDJ's Instagramthat Butch \\\"has been threatened with death, torture and rape, and has also been the target of numerous anti-Semitic, homophobic, sexist and grossophobic insults.\\\"\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 2.972496573081166e-11, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\", \"score\": 0.999998591492468, \"rank\": 1.4085095405630302e-06, \"text\": \"Audrey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2990454979839601e-12, \"text\": \"anti-Semitic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lawyer\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"theDJ's Instagramthat Butch\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"torture\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Msellati said the complaint was filed with the Paris prosecutor's office, which must then decide whether it warrants a formal police investigation.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1056, \"titl