 her segment of the show.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"love activist\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver headdress\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"a halo\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"a party\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"her segment\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drag artists, dancers and others flanked Butch on both sides.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Drag artists\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Catholic bishops and others were among those who said Christians had been hurt and offended.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1997, \"end\": 2003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9023322197428885, \"rank\": 0.10795077788299817, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2004, \"end\": 2012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9984887925943101, \"rank\": 0.00151339313423341, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5505239131609829, \"rank\": 0.7805202192601255, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Olympics organizers have said there was \\\"never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group\\\" and that the intent was to \\\"celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"the intent\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly has said he saw the moment as a celebration of diversity, and the table on which Butch spun her tunes as a tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9023322197428885, \"rank\": 0.10795077788299817, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"a celebration\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"her tunes\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"a tribute\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" Jolly said.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Performer Philippe Katerine,who appeared in the next scenepainted blue and nearly nude in a tribute to Dionysus, also told Le Monde newspaper that \\\"The Last Supper\\\" had not been referenced at all in preparations for the overall sketch.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2609, \"end\": 2626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe Katerine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\"}, {\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.615844608618618e-18, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 2722, \"end\": 2730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Monde\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tribute\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall sketch\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statement said Butch has been \\\"the target of an extremely violent campaign of cyber-harrassment and defamation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The statement\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"an extremely violent campaign\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"cyber-harrassment\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"defamation\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement of her own, also posted on Instagram, Butch said: \\\"Whatever some may say, I exist.\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2996, \"end\": 3005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.850483738561659e-24, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"Whatever\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never been ashamed of who I am, and I take responsibility for everything - including my artistic choices.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3116}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"my artistic choices\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All my life, I have refused to be a victim: I will not shut up.\\\"\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a victim\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Msellati described Butch as in \\\"a fighting spirit\\\" - eager to defend herself and her choices, and still very proud of her participation.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Msellati\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3239}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3255}, {\"ngram\": \"a fighting spirit\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"her choices\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"her participation\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has no regrets, even now,\\\" the lawyer said.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no regrets\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"the lawyer\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her lawyer's statement said legal complaints would be filed regardless of \\\"whether committed by French nationals or foreigners and intends to prosecute anyone who tries to intimidate her in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3514, \"end\": 3520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9023322197428885, \"rank\": 0.10795077788299817, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her lawyer's statement\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3440}, {\"ngram\": \"legal complaints\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"foreigners\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3544}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said she \\\"was extremely honored\\\" to perform in Friday's ceremony and \\\"my heart is still full of joy.\\\"\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Friday's ceremony\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3704}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am committed, and I am proud.\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Proud of who I am, of what I am, and of what I embody, both for my loved ones and for millions of French people.\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3860, \"end\": 3873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my loved ones\", \"from\": 3826, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My France is France !\\\"\", \"from\": 3875, \"to\": 3897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3878, \"end\": 3884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9900108581751051, \"rank\": 0.005367672390871333, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3888, \"end\": 3894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9900108581751051, \"rank\": 0.005367672390871333, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she wrote.\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"